WEBVTT

00:01:29.706 --> 00:01:30.918
who are at risk.

00:01:30.942 --> 00:01:33.959
The general population
doesn't appear to be at great risk.

00:01:33.983 --> 00:01:38.126
[What pre-existing medical conditions
put people at higher risk?]

00:01:38.150 --> 00:01:39.309
First of all,

00:01:39.333 --> 00:01:43.133
pulmonary disease existing
as a comorbidity is also important.

00:01:43.157 --> 00:01:45.661
In general, the elderly
are at greater risk,

00:01:45.685 --> 00:01:47.768
especially those over 70,

00:01:47.792 --> 00:01:50.860
because their immune systems
are not as effective

00:01:50.884 --> 00:01:52.447
as they might have once been,

00:01:52.471 --> 00:01:55.289
and they are more
susceptible to infections.

00:01:55.313 --> 00:01:58.773
In addition, in some instances in China,

00:01:58.797 --> 00:02:02.075
